('FP7ICT_EC_funding', 'All_partners', 'euro', 'EC FUNDING', 'Total value of EC funding to participants in FP7-ICT projects', 'Total EC funding to participants in FP7-ICT projects', 'Research and Development', 'Value of European Commission funding committed through grant agreements signed, during the reference year, with participants in ICT research projects under the EU’s Seventh Framework Programme (FP7). Projects under negotiation are not included.', 'MIS', 93),
