('FP7ICT_afxp', 'All_partners', 'euro', 'derived var', 'Average EC funding per participation in FP7-ICT projects', 'Average EC funding per participation', 'Research and Development', 'EC funding is the funding committed by the European Commission through grant agreements signed during the reference year. The indicator measure the average EC funding attributed to each partner participation in a specific project.', 'MIS', 105),
